                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180218-82-off426 t18180218-82-crimeloc429"></join>. On the 28th of January, I saw the prisoner take the bacon out of my shop window, at eight o'clock at night. I was behind the counter; I ran out, and secured him; he threw it down.</p>
